Chauness Chauzje Choosha (amụrụ na 31 Disemba 1992) bụ onye na-agba ọsọ na Zambia
O sonyere na 2012 IAAF World Indoor Championships ebe o guzobere ndekọ mba Zambia ọhụrụ na mita 60, e wepụrụ ya na ọkara ikpeazụ nke mita 100 na African Championships in Athletics
Choosha ruru eru maka 2012 Summer Olympics site na wildcard ma erughị eru maka agba nke mbụ nke 100 mita.
A mụrụ Choosha na 31 Disemba 1992 na Monze, Zambia. Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na Musuku High School
Choosha mere egwuregwu mba ụwa mbụ ya na afo 2012 IAAF World Indoor Championships na mita 60, ma setịpụ ihe ndekọ mba Zambia ọhụrụ na ọzụzụ ahụ, na oge nke 8.19 sekọnd

Otú ọ dị, ọ mechara nke asatọ (na nke ikpeazụ) na okpomọkụ ya ma ọ gaghị na ọkara ikpeazụ. O mechara gaa Benin iji sọọ mpi na afo 2012 African Championships in Athletics ebe o sonyere na mita 100 wee ruo eru maka ọkara ikpeazụ na oge nke 12:72 sekọnd, mana e wepụrụ ya na asọmpi mgbe ọkara ikpeazụ gasịrị. Phiri sonyekwara na mita 200 mana ọ banyeghị na ọkara ikpeazụ mgbe ọ gwụchara nke ikpeazụ na okpomọkụ ya na nke 30 n'ozuzu.

Choosha ruru eru maka afo 2012 Summer Olympics na London site na wildcard mgbe onye na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge Tonny Wamulwa merụrụ ahụ n'ihe mberede okporo ụzọ izu atọ tupu egwuregwu ahụ amalite. O sonyere na 100 mita ụmụ nwanyị na agba nke mbụ n'ụbọchị nke atọ n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ ma bụrụ onye a dọtara na okpomọkụ nke mbụ, na-emecha nke anọ n'ime ndị egwuregwu asatọ, na oge nke 12:29 sekọnd

Ka ọ na-erule afọ 2016, oge ahụ bụ nke kachasị mma. Ọ nọ n'ihu Afa Ismail si Maldivies (12.52 sekọnd) na Rima Taha nke Jọdan (12.66 sekọnd), na okpomọkụ nke Feta Ahamada nke Comoros (11.81 sekọnd). N'ozuzu, ọ mechara nke 57 n'ime ndị asọmpi 78, ọ gakwaghị n'agba nke mbụ n'ihi na oge ya kachasị ọsọ bụ 0.05 sekọnd nwayọ karịa onye na-eme egwuregwu kachasị nwayọ nke gara n'ihu.
